title: Police fire tear gas at protesters near Parliament
body_lines: Police have tear gas and water cannons to disperse protesters near the parliament entry road at Polduwa Junction in Battaramulla, Ada Derana reporter said.

The Inter-University Students’ Federation (ISUF) has been staging a protest at the entrance road to parliament near the Diyatha Uyana in Battamulla since yesterday, demanding that the President and the government steps down.
